Step 6: Pin Count Prevents Mid-Operation Eviction

div.p: Frame 0: SKIP (PinCount=2 > 0) Frame 1: Candidate (LRU=10:45:21) Frame 2: BEST VICTIM (LRU=10:44:15) Frame 3: SKIP (PinCount=1 > 0)
0x000000 Page 0 (header) 0x001000 Page 1 (schema) ... 0x02A000 Page 42 READ FROM HERE ...
A page with PinCount > 0 is never selected as an eviction victim. This prevents use-after-free bugs where a page is modified after eviction.
